## 📌 Milestone 3: Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

### 🎯 Objective
Identify patterns, trends, and insights from the cleaned dataset.

### 📊 Key Analysis Performed
- Ticket volume over time
- Priority-wise ticket distribution
- Status breakdown (Open, Closed, Pending)
- Average resolution time
- SLA compliance analysis

### 📈 Visualizations
- Bar charts for ticket distribution
- Line charts for trends over time
- Pie charts for category proportions
- Heatmaps for issue patterns

### 🔍 Key Insights
- High number of tickets in specific categories
- Delay in resolving high-priority tickets
- Peak ticket creation during certain periods
- SLA breaches in specific teams

### ⚠️ Observations
- Some teams consistently underperform
- Certain issue types take longer to resolve

### ✅ Outcome
Extracted actionable insights to guide dashboard creation and decision-making.
